### Create merchant (HUF default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/merchants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teszt Bolt Kft.",
  "email": "teszt@bolt.hu"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("merchantId", response.body.id);
%}

### Create merchant (EUR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/merchants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Euro Shop Zrt.",
  "email": "euro@shop.hu",
  "currency": "EUR"
}

### Create merchant – validation error (missing email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/merchants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hiányzó Email Kft."
}

### Create merchant – duplicate email
POST {{baseUrl}}/merchants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Duplikált Email Kft.",
  "email": "teszt@bolt.hu"
}

### Get merchant
GET {{baseUrl}}/merchants/{{merchantId}}

### Get merchant – not found
GET {{baseUrl}}/merchants/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
